flowchart LR
  %% A minimal five-node flow for README quickstarts.
  Idea[Product Idea]:::generic-user
  API[Backend API]:::generic-api
  Worker[Background Worker]:::generic-server
  Database[Application Database]:::generic-database
  Dashboard[Admin Dashboard]:::generic-browser

  Idea -->|Submit| API
  API -->|Queue Job| Worker
  Worker -->|Persist Result| Database
  Database -->|Read Metrics| Dashboard
